    location: 'Stockholm, Sweden',
    logo: 'aws',
    bullets: [
      'Sole TAM for three of the largest Nordic enterprises spanning logistics, telecom, and gaming, each running mission-critical workloads on AWS at scale.',
      'Led FinOps programmes across all three accounts: rightsizing, Savings Plans, Reserved Instance strategy, and Compute Optimizer adoption, driving significant annual cost reductions without sacrificing performance.',
      'Delivered Well-Architected Framework Reviews across reliability, security, cost, and performance pillars; produced remediation roadmaps adopted by engineering leads.',
      'Owned monthly Operational Reviews tracking SLO burn, incident trends, and open risks, presenting board-level summaries to CTO and VP Engineering stakeholders.',
      'Led P1 and P2 incident management: coordinated AWS service teams, maintained customer communication under pressure, and authored post-incident reports with root-cause analysis and prevention plans.',
