    title: 'Solution Architect · Senior Solution Integrator',
    company: 'Ericsson Group',
    period: 'Jan 2012 – Apr 2019',
    location: 'Stockholm, Sweden / Gurgaon, India',
    logo: 'ericsson',
    bullets: [
      'Led IoT Orchestration and Accelerator platform integration across AWS, Azure, and OpenStack; delivered end-to-end IoT device provisioning, data collection, analytics, and service enablement for enterprise customers across SaaS, IaaS, and PaaS deployment models.',
      'Designed and delivered a Private Cloudified LTE-in-a-Box solution, enabling operators to spin up a full LTE network stack in a single system for rapid trials; built the CI/CD automation using SaltStack, Ansible, Jenkins, and shell scripting on RedHat Linux.',
      'Architected and deployed Traffic Optimisation solutions for STC (Saudi Arabia) and Swisscom (Switzerland); performed customer traffic profiling and solution tuning to maximise compression and throughput on live mobile networks.',
      'Deployed and acceptance-tested Traffic Optimisation at Digi Malaysia, integrating the Ericsson Cloud Environment with optimisation components and conducting full traffic profiling and solution validation.',
